Description_lang: The duration of your active demon form is extended by ${$s1/1000}.1 sec per $s2 Fury spent.

description_blz.en_US: The duration of your active demon form is extended by 0.1 sec per 12 Fury spent.
description_blz.es_MX: La duración de tu Forma de demonio activa se extiende 0.1 s por cada 12 p. de furia gastados.
description_blz.pt_BR: A duração da sua forma de demônio ativa é estendida em 0,1 s a cada 12 de Fúria gasta.
description_blz.de_DE: Verlängert die Dauer eurer aktiven Dämonengestalt pro 12 verbrauchtem Jähzorn um 0,1.
description_blz.en_GB: The duration of your active demon form is extended by 0.1 sec per 12 Fury spent.

description_blz.fr_FR: La durée de votre forme de démon active est augmentée de 0,1 s par tranche de 12 points de fureur dépensés.

description_blz.ko_KR: 소모한 격노 12당 활성화된 악마 형상의 지속시간이 0.1초만큼 증가합니다.
description_blz.zh_TW: 每消耗12點魔怒後，作用中的惡魔形態持續時間延長0.1秒。
description_blz.zh_CN: 每消耗12点恶魔之怒，你激活的恶魔形态的持续时间就会延长0.1秒。
